### Phase 6: Statistical Methods Summary

All implemented in `/Users/charlesvictormahouve/Documents/GitHub/africandatalayer/lib/server/snapshotEngine.ts`:

| Method | Formula | Usage |
|--------|---------|-------|
| **Moving Average (4-week)** | `MA = sum(last_4_values) / 4` | Smoothed trend line on point count chart |
| **Week-over-Week Growth** | `WoW = (current - previous) / previous` | Trend indicators, summary cards |
| **Z-Score Anomaly** | `z = (x - mean_8w) / stddev_8w` | Flag when `|z| > 2`; stored in `anomaly_flags` |
| **Linear Trend Projection** | `y = mx + b` from last N weeks via least-squares | Optional: shown as dashed line on charts |

The z-score uses an 8-week rolling window (the most recent 8 `snapshot_stats` rows for each vertical). Anomalies are pre-computed during the cron job and stored so the dashboard does not need to re-calculate.

